Package org.semanticweb.vlog4j.core.model.implementation

Class AtomImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.semanticweb.vlog4j.core.model.implementation.AtomImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Atom
    public class AtomImpl
extends Object
implements Atom
    Implements Atom objects. An atom is a formula of the form P(t1,...,tn) for P a Predicate name, and t1,...,tn some Terms. The number of terms corresponds to the Predicate arity.
    Author:
    david.carral@tu-dresden.de, Markus Kr√∂tzsch
